description: The moment generating function of the limiting distribution of the number of comparisons in quicksort can be written in the form M(t) = m(-2*t)/(exp(2*gamma*t)*Gamma(1 + 2*t)) for |t| < 1/2, where m(z) = Sum_{n >= 0} B(n)*z^n/n! for |z| < 1. This sequence gives the numerators of the rational numbers B(n) for n >= 0.
